(define/contract (check-strings s1 s2)
  (-> string? string? boolean?)
  (let ([len (string-length s1)])
    (let loop ([i 0] [even-counts (make-hash)] [odd-counts (make-hash)])
      (cond
        [(= i len)
         (and (equal? even-counts (make-hash))
              (equal? odd-counts (make-hash)))]
        [else
         (let* ([char1 (string-ref s1 i)]
                [char2 (string-ref s2 i)]
                [counts (if (even? i) even-counts odd-counts)])
           (hash-update! counts char1 add1 0)
           (hash-update! counts char2 sub1 0)
           (loop (add1 i) even-counts odd-counts))]))))

(define (add1 x) (+ x 1))
(define (sub1 x) (- x 1))
